{
  "texts": [
    "In the testing phase, the patch classification accuracy using YOLOv5+ResNet50 was 97.2%.",
    "A confusion matrix was used to evaluate the model's performance as shown in Fig. 7.",
    "We evaluated the performance of the proposed classification by comparing its results with different state-of-the-art grade classification methods.",
    "The result of the comparison with state-of-the-art techniques is shown in Table 7.",
    "The results show that the proposed model, which is based on the hybrid of Yolov5 and Resnet50, performs better than other state-of-the-art methods (Fig. 8)."
  ]
}